</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/h0xrdfQKLyc" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/24/iphone-13-pro-2/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-13-pro-2</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>中國消費者愛 iPhone 13   新機預訂數量已超 iPhone 12</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/9QAXIBpBP9I/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Sep 2021 05:10:01 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[作者忘記分類]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1062116</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>在 9 月 24 日正式上市的 iPhone 13 系列，據悉受到中國消費者熱捧，有中國媒體表示單單訂購數量就超過 500 萬部，超越了去年推出的 iPhone 12 系列。當中電子商貿平台京東預售數字超過了 300 萬部，其他正規銷售渠道如 Apple 官網、天貓和蘇寧等都錄得好成績。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>在 9 月 24 日正式上市的 iPhone 13 系列，據悉受到中國消費者熱捧，有中國媒體表示單單訂購數量就超過 500 萬部，超越了去年推出的 iPhone 12 系列。當中電子商貿平台京東預售數字超過了 300 萬部，其他正規銷售渠道如 Apple 官網、天貓和蘇寧等都錄得好成績。</p><p><span id="more-1062116"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/26/volvo-ditches-leather-in-evs/life-tech/auto/attachment/9024-5a/" rel="attachment wp-att-1062147"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062147" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9024-5a-547x580.jpg" alt="" width="547" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9024-5a-547x580.jpg 547w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/9024-5a.jpg 690w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 547px" /></a></p><p>在 iPhone 13 系列接受預訂首日，Apple 中國官網因為消費者湧入導致不勝負荷，微博甚至因此出現熱搜詞（hashtag）「#蘋果官網崩了」，瀏覽次數超過 4.7 億成為熱搜榜第一位。最快出現缺貨的是 iPhone 13 Pro Max，但很快其他型號都出現同樣情況，而交付日期亦由 9 月 24 日延後至 10 月第二週或更後。</p><p>中國傳媒分析指 iPhone 13 系列受消費者熱捧的原因，是因為 Apple 的北美定價維持與上代相同，由於匯率下降而導致國行價格出現明顯下調，新機最平 5,199 人民幣起，但儲存則加倍至 128GB。此外，Apple 在中國的最強競爭對手華為，他們的旗艦 P50 系列不支援 5G，亦令消費者因此卻步。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://m.cnbeta.com/view/1182107.htm">cnbeta</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=9QAXIBpBP9I:Jow0xGX3Yeo:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=9QAXIBpBP9I:Jow0xGX3Yeo:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/9QAXIBpBP9I" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/24/iphone-13-china-sales/news/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-13-china-sales</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>真無線耳機出貨報告發表   AirPods 暴跌 Samsung 急增 4 成</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/cg8rnv0NrwY/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Sep 2021 05:09:39 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[AirPods]]></category><category><![CDATA[無線耳機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1062118</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前舉行的 Apple 秋季發佈會雖然有 iPhone 13、全新 iPad、iPad mini 和 Apple Watch，但並未有新版 AirPods 發表則令人失望。市場研究機構 Canalys 早前發表的報告亦顯示，Apple 在真無線耳機市場的第二季度出貨量出現了大跌，反映現時 AirPods 的受歡迎程度下跌。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>早前舉行的 Apple 秋季發佈會雖然有 iPhone 13、全新 iPad、iPad mini 和 Apple Watch，但並未有新版 AirPods 發表則令人失望。市場研究機構 Canalys 早前發表的報告亦顯示，Apple 在真無線耳機市場的第二季度出貨量出現了大跌，反映現時 AirPods 的受歡迎程度下跌。</p><p><span id="more-1062118"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/09/26/volvo-ditches-leather-in-evs/life-tech/auto/attachment/0924-7a/" rel="attachment wp-att-1062143"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062143" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/0924-7a.jpg 974w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>報告指全球真無線耳機的 2021 第二季度總出貨量為 5,830 萬套，較去年同期增長了 6.4%，不過 Apple 的出貨量卻錄得了 25.8% 的跌幅。這個統計將 AirPods 和 Beats 耳機合併計算，Apple 去年同期出貨量為 2,080 萬套，今年則跌至 1,550 萬套，以市佔率 26.5% 保住了市場冠軍的位置。</p><p>市場增長最高的是 Skullcandy，他們由去年第二季的 110 萬出貨量增加至今年同期的 410 萬套，而 Samsung 連同 Harman Kardon 加起來亦有 40.5% 的按年增幅，令他們僅次於小米排在真無線耳機市場的第三位。分析指 Apple 將會在稍後發表 AirPods 3，或者會帶動出貨量回升。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.techradar.com/news/global-tws-market-grows-at-64-in-q2-its-lowest-in-last-3-years">techradar</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=cg8rnv0NrwY:M8a_5ehZ-xw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=cg8rnv0NrwY:M8a_5ehZ-xw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/cg8rnv0NrwY" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/24/global-tws-market-shipment-report/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=global-tws-market-shipment-report</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Lenovo Tab P11 Plus 頂級家庭平板   11 吋超亮 IPS 熒幕 + 杜比全景聲 4 喇叭</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/FL1xN3e1aSk/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[AIpower]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Sep 2021 03:22:24 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[平板電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[Lenovo Tab P11 Plus]]></category><category><![CDATA[平板]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1058471</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>平板電腦最大優勢是利用其大畫面睇片、打機，視覺享受一流；大畫面也方便日常工作，製作簡報或開視像會議。近日 Le [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>平板電腦最大優勢是利用其大畫面睇片、打機，視覺享受一流；大畫面也方便日常工作，製作簡報或開視像會議。近日 Lenovo 就將會推出一款主打靚聲、靚畫面，兼有纖巧機身、大容量電池與搭載高速處理器的頂級家庭平板電腦 Lenovo Tab P11 Plus，滿足用家對平板電腦的各種「奄尖」需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060675 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.24.27-694x442.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="442" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.24.27-694x442.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.24.27-768x490.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.24.27.jpg 1026w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>強化打機睇片效果：11 吋 IPS 屏幕+ Dolby Atmos 4 喇叭</h2><p>睇片打機夠暢快，最緊要當然是大芒靚聲。Lenovo Tab P11 Plus 就用上了獲認證播高質播放 Netflix 的 11 吋 TDDI IPS 顯示器，解像度為 2000 x 1600，能輸出 2K 解像度畫面顯示畫質，提升睇片打機體驗。其 400 nit 屏幕亮度，讓用戶在陽光下也可觀看到畫面內容。Tap P11 Plus 更加強影音方面的設計，特別加入支援 Dolby Atmos 杜比全景聲的 4 個揚聲器，用平板來睇戲都可擁有十足臨場感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058481 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray-694x492.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="492" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray-694x492.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray-1270x900.jpg 1270w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray-768x544.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray-1536x1088.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Colourful_Gaming_Screen_Slate_gray.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060765 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.53.39-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.53.39-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.53.39-768x495.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.53.39.jpg 1001w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060766 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.31-694x415.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="415" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.31-694x415.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.31-768x460.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.31.jpg 1014w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>選購鍵盤組、觸控筆馬上投入工作</h2><p>Tab P11 Plus 亦可應用於工作上，它平板搭載 Android 11 以及 Google Play，可順利下載各種應用程式。用家可選購附有觸控板的 Lenovo 鍵盤套件，隨時將平板變身效率型手提電腦。用家亦可選配 Lenovo Precision Pen 2 具有 4096 級感壓度與傾斜檢測的操控筆，它一次充電可用 200 小時，可用以在平板繪畫或迅速書寫筆記。平板支援 Google Kids Space 與 Google Entertainment Space，俾仔女使用也能更加安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060663 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.11.10-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.11.10-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.11.10-768x519.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-16.11.10.jpg 1019w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058479 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-768x425.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001.jpg 1264w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060767 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.59-533x580.jpg" alt="" width="533" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.59-533x580.jpg 533w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.59-827x900.jpg 827w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.59-768x836.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.54.59.jpg 901w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 533px" /></p><h2>人臉辨識解鎖平板電腦</h2><p>Tab P11 Plus 內置有人臉辨識功能，用戶可毋須記憶繁複的密碼，只要望一望平板上的鏡頭，就能解鎖平板電腦。除了方便之外，也能節省你輸入密碼所需的時間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058482 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/09_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Face_Unlock_Slate_gray.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>配置、電量足夠日常應用</h2><p>Tab P11 Plus 搭載 2.05GHz MediaTek Helio G90T Tab 八核心處理器，有利於打機、用瀏覽器上網提升效率。平板內置有 4GB RAM，同時處理多項工作保持暢順，內置儲存更有 64GB，有更多空間儲存多媒體影片、公司文件。平板更配備 7700mAh 電池，充電一次可使用長達 15 小時，依照使用情況可兩天甚至幾天才充電一次。往後 Lenovo 更會推出一款搭載有 6GB RAM + 128GB 內置儲存、可連接 LTE 上網的款式。</p><p>機身方面，Lenovo Tab P11 Plus 用上 Slate Grey 板岩灰配色、鋁合金設計的纖巧機身，螢幕周邊的邊框特幼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1058476 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray-1001x900.jpg" alt="" width="1001" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray-1001x900.jpg 1001w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray-645x580.jpg 645w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray-768x690.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray-1536x1381.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01_Tab_P11_Plus_Hero_Front_Back_Slate_gray.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1060658 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-900x900.png" alt="" width="900" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward-1536x1536.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/02_P11_Arno_Tour_Rear_Facing_Forward.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1060660 size-large" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-900x900.jpg" alt="" width="900" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04_P11_Arno_Tour_Right_Profile.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><h2>可選購之配件</h2><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060768 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.55.35-694x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.55.35-694x580.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.55.35-768x641.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.55.35.jpg 995w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1060773 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.58-694x504.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="504" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.58-694x504.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.58-768x558.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.58.jpg 917w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲保護套</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1060770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.09-694x429.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="429" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.09-694x429.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.09-768x474.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-16-18.56.09.jpg 962w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲鍵盤套裝</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058487 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0008-694x477.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="477" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0008-694x477.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0008-768x528.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0008.jpg 1251w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Lenovo Precision Pen 2 觸控筆</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1058485 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0010-1-694x479.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="479" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0010-1-694x479.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0010-1-768x530.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0010-1.jpg 1072w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充電座</p></p><div class="feedflare">
